snippet.textDisplay: Traditional folk music of any place is the nectar of that region which defines it in real sense. I have heard Bhanwari Ji before and words fall short when it comes to her description. I am thankful to Coke studio that they have called them as guests. We are lucky to listen them, and I hope the various folk artists could meet their economic needs better, when they join the popular platform like this. Jai Hind!
